From: L. David Baron <dbaron@dbaron.org>

Bug 978608:  Shut down pango's fontmap cleanly and shut down fontconfig, #if CLEANUP_MEMORY.

This bumps the minimum required pango version to 1.22, released 29 Sep 2008.

